operations using the Android KeyStore system. It is provided as a
general-purpose cryptographic signing library and does NOT constitute:

- A qualified electronic signature tool under eIDAS Regulation (EU) 910/2014
- A FIPS 140-2 or FIPS 140-3 validated cryptographic module
- A certified security product under any national or international scheme
- Legal, regulatory, or compliance advice of any kind

